Package: count
Type: Package
Title: This package counts the missing values in a column by group and displays them as a count
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Daniel Robinson
Maintainer: The package maintainer <daniero@ubc.ca.mail>
Description: count is a package created for STAT 545 assignment B2, making an R package. This package contains functions that can aid in data analysis  and data visualization. count_all_missing_by_group is a function that counts  missing values. for all columns by group, providing a summary tibble of missing  value (i.e. NAs) as output. This function is valauable for early assesments of data, spot-checking for missing values among levels and categories 
